============================================
Name: sample-dynamodb
Description:
  The sample-dynamodb is a Node.Js scripted
  interface with a local version of
  DynamoDb. It can be used to create and
  setup AWS DynamoDb by changing the connection
  information.
============================================

=================
Local Dev
=================

-------
Local DynamoDb
-------

- Download DynamoDb Local -
http://dynamodb-local.s3-website-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/dynamodb_local_latest.zip

- Run DynamoDb on your local machine -
java -Djava.library.path=./DynamoDBLocal_lib -jar DynamoDBLocal.jar -sharedDb

- DynamoDb JavaScript Shell -
http://localhost:8000/shell/

-------
NodeJs Scripted Setup
-------

node index {command}
